==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: rì yŏu suŏ sī, yè yŏu suŏ mèng
===Proverb===
'''[[日]][[有]][[所]][[思]]，[[夜]][[有]][[所]][[梦]]'''
# That which one thinks about during the day, is what one is likely to dream about at night.
===Alternate forms===
[[日有所思，夜有所夢]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])
